{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"33449-paha-tar-khara","title":"पाहा तर खरं!","description":"पक्षी आणि वटवाघळं. पतंग आणि विमानं. आपल्यापासून अगदी उंचावरच्या या अद्भुत विश्वाचा आपण शोध घेतो का? चला तर मग... या वेगवेगळे गमतीदार नमुने असणाऱ्या पुस्तकातल्या ‘वेगळी गोष्ट बाजूला काढा’  हा खेळ खेळायला तयार व्हा. ","language":"Marathi","langCode":"mr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ashlesha Mahajan"],"illustrators":["Aditi Dilip"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/33449-paha-tar-khara"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/714197/size3/b769676c4189b596ea7f2c7e00825ca4.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/714197/size6/b769676c4189b596ea7f2c7e00825ca4.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/33449/audios/story/33449-paha-tar-khara.mp3","cues":[[1,0,1.92],[2,1.92,2.8],[3,2.8,3.88],[4,3.88,5],[5,5,5.88],[6,5.88,6.72],[7,6.72,7.72],[8,7.72,8.7],[9,8.7,9.82],[10,9.82,10.56],[11,10.56,11],[12,11,12.25],[13,12.25,13.3],[14,13.3,13.96],[15,13.96,14.35],[16,14.35,15.16],[17,15.16,17.56],[18,17.56,22],[19,22,23],[20,23,24.2],[21,24.2,25.6],[22,25.6,26.15],[23,26.15,27.9],[24,27.9,28.7],[25,28.7,29.7],[26,29.7,30.76],[27,30.76,31.5],[28,31.5,32.25],[29,32.25,33.35],[30,33.35,33.98],[31,33.98,37.64],[32,37.64,40.44],[33,40.44,41.5],[34,41.5,42.5],[35,42.5,43.68],[36,43.68,44.16],[37,44.16,45.38],[38,45.38,45.5],[39,45.5,45.94],[40,45.94,47.48],[41,47.48,48],[42,48,48.8],[43,48.8,49.68],[44,49.68,50.08],[45,50.08,51],[46,51,52],[47,52,52.44],[48,52.44,52.8],[49,52.8,53.96],[50,53.96,54.48],[51,54.48,54.92],[52,54.92,58.2],[53,58.2,61.16],[54,61.16,61.72],[55,61.72,62.72],[56,62.72,63.32],[5